        dc:description           "Fig. 28. Tafana pittieri sp. nov. (A, C–E =holotype, ♂, AMNH; B, F–G=paratype, ♀, AMNH). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, dorsal view. C. Left palp, ventral view. D. Left palp, retrolateral view. E. Left palp, dorsal view. F. Epigynum, ventral view. G. Vulva, dorsal view. Abbreviations: A=atrium; ABE= apophysis of base of the embolus; CD=copulatory ducts; CO =copulatory opening; E =embolus; FD =fertilization ducts; H =hood; LL=lateral lobes; RTA=retrolateral tibial apophysis; S1 =primary spermathecae; S2 =secondary spermathecae; T = tegulum; VTP=ventral tegular process. Scale bars: A–B =3.5 mm; C–D =0.4 mm; F–G=0.25 mm." ;
